{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":218}],"windowDisplayName":"？？？","body":"各位，好久不见。\n之前演出的时候，承蒙大家关照。\n我是练习生芹泽澪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":218,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"噢，小澪。\n好久不见，你是不是变成熟了？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event135-02-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":218}],"windowDisplayName":"澪","body":"我觉得应该没有……\n总之，今后也请多多关照了。\n下一位是濑理奈，自我介绍一下吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":218,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":219}],"windowDisplayName":"濑理奈","body":"好的！大家还好吗？\n我是天使系偶像小濑理，山濑濑理奈！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":219,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"天使系偶像……？\n之前联合练习的时候，\n你好像没有这样介绍自己吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressi